<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_SP49_CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging" s="360183">
  <T n="name">0x6894BE48<!--Crystal Charging--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d1535764141b</T>
      <T n="text">0x1FE8A0F1<!--Gemstones and Jewelry crafted with crystals can be <b><font color='#199C2C'>charged</font></b> to unlock the crystalâ€™s innate <b><font color='#199C2C'>power</font></b>! Each crystal has <b><font color='#199C2C'>unique properties</font></b> to discover, from boosting skills and relationships to lucid dreams and power over Death itself!\n\nAll you need is the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Mystical Moonlight Crystal Grid</font></b> and some moonlight.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d15357641418</T>
      <T n="text">0x9623D86E<!--Place your Gemstones and Jewelry on a Crystal Grid <b><font color='#199C2C'>outdoors between 7pm and 7am</font></b> to charge them. You can do this by <b><font color='#199C2C'>dragging</font></b> items to the Grid, by selecting <b><font color='#199C2C'>Charge Items</font></b> on the Grid, or selecting <b><font color='#199C2C'>Charge on Crystal Grid</font></b> on the Gemstone or Jewelry piece.\n\nThe Crystal Grid has a helpful <b><font color='#199C2C'>tooltip</font></b> which explains if it is charging or not, what speed it is charging at, and the status of the individual items on the Grid. You can also look out for the <b><font color='#199C2C'>magical glow</font></b> of a fully charged crystal!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d15357641419</T>
      <T n="text">0x34B9EA6F<!--The Crystal Grid charging speed ebbs and flows with the <b><font color='#199C2C'>phases of the moon</font></b>. The full moon will charge your Gemstones and Jewelry in no time, but expect longer charging times during the new moon.\n\nThere are <b><font color='#199C2C'>special places</font></b>, like Sylvan Glade and Forgotten Grotto, where the Crystal Grid can charge all day.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d1535764141e</T>
      <T n="text">0xD7F4C93C<!--When you're done charging your Gemstones and Jewelry, you can <b><font color='#199C2C'>pick them up</font></b> from the Crystal Grid and place it in your Sim's home or inventory, or make your Sim wear them.\n\nGemstones will start to <b><font color='#199C2C'>lose their charge</font></b> as soon as they stop charging. Jewelry only loses its charge when worn with the Sim's current outfit. You can check the <b><font color='#199C2C'>tooltip</font></b> of the item to see how much charge is remaining.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d1535764141f</T>
      <T n="text">0x4493CF58<!--The <b><font color='#199C2C'>power</font></b> of a charged Gemstone or Jewelry piece depends on what <b><font color='#199C2C'>crystal</font></b> it was made from. Each crystal has a unique power.\n\nGemstones will spread their power to <b><font color='#199C2C'>everyone closeby</font></b>. Jewelry will give their power to the Sim <b><font color='#199C2C'>wearing</font></b> it with their current outfit.\n\nSims under the influence of a charged crystal will get a special <b><font color='#199C2C'>Moodlet</font></b>. Read the description to learn more about its powers!\n\nMost Crystal powers have a passive effect, but items crafted with Jet also have a special interaction on the item itself.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_CrystalCharging_6.png">2f7d0004:00000000:4247d1535764141c</T>
      <T n="text">0x791D7688<!--Sims that complete the Crystal Crafter Aspiration will be rewarded with the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Attuned</font></b> trait. Their worn Jewelry will lose charge <b><font color='#199C2C'>slower</font></b>. They can also use the interaction <b><font color='#199C2C'>Absorb Energy</font></b> on a charged Gemstone or Jewelry piece to drain its charge in exchange for a boost to their Energy need.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
